urrent_page\"></span> of <span class=\"mlp_total_page\"></span></div>\n                    <a id=\"mlp_next_arrow\" class=\"right arrow mlp_arrow_button mlp_next_arrow\" href=\"#\">></a>\n                </div>\n\n\n                <div class=\"clear show-on-tablets\"></div>\n                <div class=\"clear show-on-mobiles\"></div>\n\n\n               <div id=\"mlp_info\" class=\"twelve columns\">\n                    <div id=\"full-gallery-title\"><span class=\"mlp_current_title\"></span></div>\n                    <div id=\"full-gallery-desc\">\n                        <span class=\"mlp_current_desc\"></span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n</span><p>The post <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/week-in-pictures-89/\">Week in pictures</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca\">Macleans.ca</a>.</p>","wfw:commentRss":"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/week-in-pictures-89/feed/","slash:comments":"0"},{"title":"Maclean’s on the Hill: The first anniversary edition","link":"http://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/macleans-on-the-hill-the-first-anniversary-edition/","comments":"http://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/macleans-on-the-hill-the-first-anniversary-edition/#comments","pubDate":"Sat, 31 Jan 2015 01:00:51 +0000","dc:creator":"macleans.ca","category":["Ottawa","Podcast","Politics","Maclean's on the Hill"],"guid":"http://www.macleans.ca/?p=672661","description":"<p>In this show taped live at U of O, MPs, Paul Wells and Susan Delacourt preview 2015 in politics</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/macleans-on-the-hill-the-first-anniversary-edition/\">Maclean’s on the Hill: The first anniversary edition</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca\">Macleans.ca</a>.</p>","content:encoded":"<span itemprop=\"articleBody\" class=\"entry-content\"><p><a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/ON-THE-HILL.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-514329\" alt=\"podcast\" src=\"http://www.macleans.ca/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/ON-THE-HILL.jpg\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" /></a></p>\n<p>Each week, the <em>Maclean’s</em> politics team and Rogers radio’s Cormac Mac Sweeney sit down to hash out the week’s news in Ottawa.</p>\n<p>This week, we celebrated the first anniversary of the podcast with a live taping at the University of Ottawa. (Rough cut and photos: <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/news/canada/join-us-for-a-live-taping-of-macleans-on-the-hill/\">here.</a>) We spoke with Conservative minister <strong>Pierre Poilievre,</strong> NDP MP <strong>Jean Crowder,</strong> Liberal MP <strong>Irwin Cotler</strong> and Equal Voice’s <strong>Nancy Peckford</strong> about what to expect from this year’s election. Then <strong>Paul Wells</strong> and <strong>Susan Delacourt </strong>talked about where federal politics stands with nine months to go.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/ca/podcast/macleans.ca-podcast/id884074529?mt=2\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Subscribe on iTunes today,</strong></a> or play below, on <a href=\"http://www.stitcher.com/podcast/macleans-on-the-hill\" target=\"_blank\">Stitcher</a>.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/188726750&color=ff5500&auto_play=false&hide_related=false&show_comments=true&show_user=true&show_reposts=false\" height=\"166\" width=\"100%\" frameborder=\"no\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">THE HEADLINES</h1>\n<ul class=\"block-grid mobile two-up\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/politics/on-iraq-questions-of-combat-cost-and-clarity/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.macleans.ca/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/MAC38_INSIDE_OTTAWA_FEATURE011-300x300.jpg\" width=\"100%\" /> <strong>ON IRAQ</strong></a><br />\n<em style=\"line-height: 19px;\">Where’s the constructive dialogue?</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/patriotism-was-the-last-refuge-of-scoundrels-youtubes-next/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.macleans.ca/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/MAC07_247_FEATURE.jpg\" width=\"100%\" /> <strong>ON CAMPAIGNS</strong></a><br />\n<em style=\"line-height: 19px;\">The PMO bets on security</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/why-pm-wont-meet-premiers/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.macleans.ca/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/MAC06_WELLS_FEATURE01.jpg\" width=\"100%\" /> <strong>ON PREMIERS</strong></a><br />\n<em style=\"line-height: 19px;\">Why the PM won’t meet them</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/politics/justin-trudeau-with-nine-months-to-go/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.macleans.ca/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/MAC18_COSH_FEATURE.jpg\" width=\"100%\" /> <strong>ON TRUDEAU</strong></a><br />\n<em style=\"line-height: 19px;\">Nine month from E-Day</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/victims-of-communism-memorial-designs-worried-chief-justice/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.macleans.ca/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/MAC06_VICTIMS_OF_COMMUNISM_THUMBNAIL.jpg\" width=\"100%\" /> <strong>ON MEMORIALS</strong></a><br />\n<em style=\"line-height: 19px;\">The Chief Justice’s warning</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/politics/questionperiodlive/qp-live-even-talking-oil-yik-yak/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.macleans.ca/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/QP-Live-300x300.jpg\" width=\"100%\" /> <strong>ON OIL</strong></a><br />\n<em style=\"line-height: 19px;\">Everyone’s talking about it</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em style=\"line-height: 19px;\"></em><a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/episode49.mp3\">Download the podcast here. </a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</span><p>The post <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/macleans-on-the-hill-the-first-anniversary-edition/\">Maclean’s on the Hill: The first anniversary edition</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca\">Macleans.ca</a>.</p>","wfw:commentRss":"http://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/macleans-on-the-hill-the-first-anniversary-edition/feed/","slash:comments":"0"},{"title":"This Week in Pictures","link":"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/7-days-in-15-photos-4/","comments":"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/7-days-in-15-photos-4/#comments","pubDate":"Fri, 30 Jan 2015 22:55:42 +0000","dc:creator":"Jessica Darmanin","category":"Photo","guid":"http://www.macleans.ca/?p=672799","description":"<p>7 days in 15 photos</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/7-days-in-15-photos-4/\">This Week in Pictures</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca\">Macleans.ca</a>.</p>","content:encoded":"<span itemprop=\"articleBody\" class=\"entry-content\"><script type='text/javascript'>var image_max_height = \"500\";</script><script type='text/javascript'>var imagesArray = [{\"id\":672743,\"mlpId\":\"6411\",\"src\":\"http:\\/\\/www.macleans.ca\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/01\\/01_RTR4NFUL1-660x460.jpg\",\"width\":660,\"height\":460,\"medSrc\":\"http:\\/\\/www.macleans.ca\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/01\\/01_RTR4NFUL1-150x150.jpg\",\"medWidth\":150,\"medHeight\":150,\"smallSrc\":\"http:\\/\\/www.macleans.ca\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/01\\/01_RTR4NFUL1-150x150.jpg\",\"smallWidth\":150,\"smallHeight\":150,\"tagSlugs\":\"\",\"tagNames\":\"\",\"title\":\"Gaza City, Gaza Strip\",\"caption\":\"\",\"loaded\":false,\"description\":\"A boy arrives at a military-style graduation ceremony for youths trained at a Hamas-run \\\"liberation youths camp\\\" for Palestinians aged 15 to 21. About 17,000 youths have graduated from such camps, meant to prepare them to \\\"confront any possible Israeli attack,\\\" Hamas offi