 <span class=\"mlp_current_desc\"></span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n</span><p>The post <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/news/weekinphotos/week-in-pictures-86/\">Week in Pictures</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca\">Macleans.ca</a>.</p>","wfw:commentRss":"http://www.macleans.ca/news/weekinphotos/week-in-pictures-86/feed/","slash:comments":"0"},{"title":"Paul Wells: ‘Charlie Hebdo was here’","link":"http://www.macleans.ca/news/world/video-charlie-hebdo-was-here/","comments":"http://www.macleans.ca/news/world/video-charlie-hebdo-was-here/#comments","pubDate":"Fri, 09 Jan 2015 02:05:09 +0000","dc:creator":"Paul Wells","category":["Video","World","Charlie Hebdo","Paris","Paris shooting"],"guid":"http://www.macleans.ca/?p=662299","description":"<p>Video: Our political editor reports from Paris on the evening of a day of mourning</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/news/world/video-charlie-hebdo-was-here/\">Paul Wells: ‘Charlie Hebdo was here’</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca\">Macleans.ca</a>.</p>","content:encoded":"<span itemprop=\"articleBody\" class=\"entry-content\"><div itemprop=\"video\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/VideoObject\"><div style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<object id=\"413409657\" class=\"BrightcoveExperience\"><param name=\"bgcolor\" value=\"#FFFFFF\" />\n<param name=\"wmode\" value=\"transparent\" />\n<param name=\"templateReadyHandler\" value=\"rdm_foundation_bc_onTemplateReady\" />\n<param name=\"templateLoadHandler\" value=\"rdm_foundation_bc_onTemplateLoaded\" />\n<param name=\"includeAPI\" value=\"true\" />\n<param name=\"isVid\" value=\"true\" />\n<param name=\"isUI\" value=\"true\" />\n<param name=\"dynamicStreaming\" value=\"true\" />\n<param name=\"width\" value=\"640\" />\n<param name=\"height\" value=\"360\" /><param name=\"playerID\" value=\"781201057001\" /><param name=\"@videoPlayer\" value=\"3978625941001\" /></object><meta itemprop='name' content='Maclean's - Charlie Hebdo was here - Paul Wells in Paris' /><meta itemprop='thumbnail' content='http://newsandbusiness.rogersdigitalmedia.com.edgesuite.net/bcassets/13639244001/201501/1901/13639244001_3978668694001_Paul-Wells-in-Paris-Frame-grab.jpg?pubId=13639244001' /><meta itemprop='duration' content='PT1M55S' /><meta itemprop='description' content='Maclean's - Charlie Hebdo was here - Paul Wells in Paris' /></div>\n<p><em>Maclean’s</em> Politics Editor Paul Wells reports from Paris on a national day of mourning. A day earlier, 10 journalists and two police officers were gunned down in the offices of Charlie Hebdo, a satirical news weekly. The killers remain at large.</p>\n<p>Follow Wells and his continuing coverage on Twitter at @inklessPW:</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" lang=\"en\"><p><a href=\"http://t.co/MlEaVk9MyV\">pic.twitter.com/MlEaVk9MyV</a></p>\n<p>— Paul Wells (@InklessPW) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/InklessPW/status/553239889119309824\">January 8, 2015</a></p></blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" lang=\"en\"><p>Place de la République. <a href=\"http://t.co/0Lb5BNDFkx\">pic.twitter.com/0Lb5BNDFkx</a></p>\n<p>— Paul Wells (@InklessPW) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/InklessPW/status/553237270116204544\">January 8, 2015</a></p></blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Related posts:</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/photos-mourning-in-the-place-de-la-republique/\">Grief and gathering in Place de la République</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/news/world/satire-demands-moral-courage/\">Satire: Use at own risk </a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/news/world/cartoonists-pay-tribute-to-charlie-hebdo/\">Cartoonists pay tribute to #CharlieHebdo</a></p>\n</span><p>The post <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/news/world/video-charlie-hebdo-was-here/\">Paul Wells: ‘Charlie Hebdo was here’</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca\">Macleans.ca</a>.</p>","wfw:commentRss":"http://www.macleans.ca/news/world/video-charlie-hebdo-was-here/feed/","slash:comments":"1"},{"title":"Photos: Grief and gathering in Place de la République","link":"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/photos-mourning-in-the-place-de-la-republique/","comments":"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/photos-mourning-in-the-place-de-la-republique/#comments","pubDate":"Thu, 08 Jan 2015 20:26:42 +0000","dc:creator":"macleans.ca","category":["Photo","Charlie Hebdo","Paris shooting"],"guid":"http://www.macleans.ca/?p=662011","description":"<p>Portraits of mourning and solidarity from Paris</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/photos-mourning-in-the-place-de-la-republique/\">Photos: Grief and gathering in Place de la République</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca\">Macleans.ca</a>.</p>","content:encoded":"<span itemprop=\"articleBody\" class=\"entry-content\"><p>With signs emblazoned with the slogan Je Suis Charlie and a throng gathered in the historic Place de la République to show that they were unafraid of this attack on their soil, thousands of Parisians gathered to grieve and stand together for the 12 lives lost in a brazen killing at satirical magazine <em>Charlie Hebdo</em>‘s offices. Photographer Nick Kozak was on the scene.</p>\n<script type='text/javascript'>var image_max_height = \"500\";</script><script type='text/javascript'>var imagesArray = [{\"id\":661927,\"mlpId\":\"6155\",\"src\":\"http:\\/\\/www.macleans.ca\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/01\\/NickKozak-Paris-010815-0153-660x439.jpg\",\"width\":660,\"height\":439,\"medSrc\":\"http:\\/\\/www.macleans.ca\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/01\\/NickKozak-Paris-010815-0153-150x150.jpg\",\"medWidth\":150,\"medHeight\":150,\"smallSrc\":\"http:\\/\\/www.macleans.ca\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2015\\/01\\/NickKozak-Paris-010815-0153-150x150.jpg\",\"smallWidth\":150,\"smallHeight\":150,\"tagSlugs\":\"\",\"tagNames\":\"\",\"title\":\"Paris, France\",\"caption\":\"(Nick Kozak photo) \",\"loaded\":false,\"description\":\"At Place de la R\\u00e9publique on Jan. 8, 2015, the day after the Charlie Hebdo massacre. (Photograph by Nick Kozak.)\",\"order\":\"1\",\"imageCount\":\"16\",\"alt\":\"\"}];</script><a name='gallery_top' id='gallery_top'></a><a name='mobile_gallery_top' id='mobile_gallery_top'></a>\n<div id='mlp_ajax_loader'><img src='http://www.macleans.ca/wp-content/plugins/media-library-plus/images/ajax-loader.gif' /></div>\n<div id=\"universal_mlp_container\">\n\n<div id=\"mlp_gallery_viewer\">\n\n\t<div id=\"mlp_nav_image_container\">\n\n\t\t<div id=\"image_container\"></div>\n\t\t<div class=\"mlp_prev_zone mlp_shadow_zone\"></div>\n\t\t<div class=\"mlp_next_zone mlp_shadow_zone\"></div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"mlp_prev_detector mlp_detector\" id=\"mlp_prev_detector\">&nbsp;</div>\n        <div class=\"mlp_next_detector mlp_detector\" id=\"mlp_next_detector\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"mlp_prev_zone mlp_arrow_container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"mlp_inner_nav\">\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\"></a>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"mlp_next_zone mlp_arrow_container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"mlp_inner_nav\">\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\"></a>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t</div>\n    <div id=\"mlp_caption\"><span class=\"mlp_current_caption\"></span></div>\n\n    <div class=\"mlp_mobile_nav show-on-phones\">\n        <div id=\"full-gallery-nav\">\n            <a id=\"mlp_prev_arrow\" class=\"left arrow mlp_arrow_button mlp_prev_arrow\" href=\"#\"><</a>\n            <a id=\"mlp_next_arrow\" class=\"right arrow mlp_arrow_button mlp_next_arrow\" href=\"#\">></a>\n        </div>\n        <div id=\"full-gallery-numbers\"><span class=\"hide-on-phones\">Photo </span><b><span class=\"mlp_current_page\"></span></b> of <b><span class=\"mlp_total_page\"></span></b></div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n            <div class=\"row\">\n\n                <div id=\"full-gallery-nav\">\n                    <a