         </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n</span><p>The post <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/year-in-pictures-celebrations-and-commemorations/\">Year in Pictures: Celebrations and commemorations</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca\">Macleans.ca</a>.</p>","wfw:commentRss":"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/year-in-pictures-celebrations-and-commemorations/feed/","slash:comments":"0"},{"title":"Year in Pictures: Weather and nature","link":"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/year-in-pictures-weather/","comments":"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/year-in-pictures-weather/#comments","pubDate":"Wed, 24 Dec 2014 13:42:21 +0000","dc:creator":"Andrew Tolson","category":["Photo","Best of 2014"],"guid":"http://www.macleans.ca/?p=655919","description":"<p>The best snaps of the amazing wrath and beauty of nature, from our Week in Pictures series</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/year-in-pictures-weather/\">Year in Pictures: Weather and nature</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca\">Macleans.ca</a>.</p>","content:encoded":"<span itemprop=\"articleBody\" class=\"entry-content\"><p>Every week, our photo editors curate the <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/tag/week-in-pictures\" target=\"_blank\">Week in Pictures series</a>, a collection of some of the most beautiful, moving, vivid, adorable and heartbreaking photos from the last seven days. As part of our <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/tag/best-of-2014\" target=\"_blank\">Best of 2014 web series</a>, we’ve assembled galleries of some of the best of those snaps. Here’s the most remarkable photos from the storms that rocked us, the disasters we endured, and the natural wonders that stunned us:</p>\n<script type='text/javascript'>var image_max_height = \"500\";</script><script type='text/javascript'>var imagesArray = [{\"id\":653961,\"mlpId\":\"5811\",\"src\":\"http:\\/\\/www.macleans.ca\\/wp-content\