s":"0"},{"title":"Year in Pictures: Animals","link":"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/year-in-pictures-animals/","comments":"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/year-in-pictures-animals/#comments","pubDate":"Tue, 23 Dec 2014 16:22:28 +0000","dc:creator":"Andrew Tolson","category":["Photo","Best of 2014"],"guid":"http://www.macleans.ca/?p=655923","description":"<p>From adorable macaques to wild horses, here are the best snaps of animals from 2014</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/year-in-pictures-animals/\">Year in Pictures: Animals</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca\">Macleans.ca</a>.</p>","content:encoded":"<span itemprop=\"articleBody\" class=\"entry-content\"><p>Every week, our photo editors curate the <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/tag/week-in-pictures\" target=\"_blank\">Week in Pictures series</a>, a collection of some of the most stunning, moving, vivid, adorable and heartbreaking photos from the last seven days. As part of our <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/tag/best-of-2014\" target=\"_blank\">Best of 2014 web series</a>, we’ve assembled galleries of some of the best of those snaps. Here’s the most remarkable photos of animals, in all their wild—sometimes profoundly cute—glory:</p>\n<script type='text/javascript'>var image_max_height = \"500\";</script><script type='text/javascript'>var imagesArray = [{\"id\":654463,\"mlpId\":\"5869\",\"src\":\"http:\\/\\/www.macleans.ca\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/12\\/MPM-Shark_Amanda_Brewer_51-660x494.jpg\",\"width\":660,\"height\":494,\"medSrc\":\"http:\\/\\/www.macleans.ca\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/12\\/MPM-Shark_Amanda_Brewer_51-150x150.jpg\",\"medWidth\":150,\"medHeight\":150,\"smallSrc\":\"http:\\/\\/www.macleans.ca\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/12\\/MPM-Shark_Amanda_Brewer_51-150x150.jpg\",\"smallWidth\":150,\"smallHeight\":150,\"tagSlugs\":\"\",\"tagNames\":\"\",\"title\":\"Seal Island, South Africa\",\"caption\":\"\",\"loaded\":false,\"d