://www.macleans.ca/?p=655887","description":"<p>The best snaps of the thrill of victory and the agony of defeat, from our Week in Pictures series</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/multimedia/photo/year-in-pictures-sports-and-competition/\">Year in Pictures: Sports and competition</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca\">Macleans.ca</a>.</p>","content:encoded":"<span itemprop=\"articleBody\" class=\"entry-content\"><p>Every week, our photo editors curate the <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/tag/week-in-pictures\" target=\"_blank\">Week in Pictures series</a>, a collection of some of the most stunning, moving, vivid, adorable and heartbreaking photos in any given week. As part of our <a href=\"http://www.macleans.ca/tag/best-of-2014\" target=\"_blank\">Best of 2014 web series</a>, we’ve assembled galleries of some of the best of those snaps. Here’s the most remarkable photos from a great year in sports, which featured both the World Cup and the Winter Olympics:</p>\n<script type='text/javascript'>var image_max_height = \"500\";</script><script type='text/javascript'>var imagesArray = [{\"id\":654119,\"mlpId\":\"5839\",\"src\":\"http:\\/\\/www.macleans.ca\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/12\\/468371167-660x459.jpg\",\"width\":660,\"height\":459,\"medSrc\":\"http:\\/\\/www.macleans.ca\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/12\\/468371167-150x150.jpg\",\"medWidth\":150,\"medHeight\":150,\"smallSrc\":\"http:\\/\\/www.macleans.ca\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2014\\/12\\/468371167-150x150.jpg\",\"smallWidth\":150,\"smallHeight\":150,\"tagSlugs\":\"\",\"tagNames\":\"\",\"title\":\"Sochi, Russia\",\"caption\":\"\",\"loaded\":false,\"description\":\"Canada's Marc-Antoine Gagnon competes in the men's moguls finals on Day 3 of the 2014 Winter Olympics at Rosa Khutor Extreme Park in Sochi, Russia (Julian Finney\\/Getty Images)\",\"order\":\"1\",\"imageCount\":\"15\",\"alt\":\"\"}];</script><a name='gallery_top' id='gallery_top'></a><a name='mobile_gallery_top' i